<lyrics>[V1]
 Ka Bawipa a nung than ti ka hngalh, A dir than lai, Vaw lei cungah, Ka
 hngalh ko zungzal nunnak a pek, A sin a um vel le thawnnak.

[C1]
   Ka hngalh, ka hngalh, Jesuh a nung than, Vawlei cung ah a dir than
   lai, Ka hngalh, ka hngalh, Nunnak Bawipa cu, Vel le thawnnak a sin a um.

[V2]
 A biakam a pelh bal lo ka hngalh, A bia a hmun, Zei tik hmanh ah,
 Thihnak nih ka pumsa tei hmanh seh, Ka hmuh than theo lai, tu hnu ah.

[C2]
   Ka hngalh, ka hngalh, Jesuh a nung than, Vawlei cung ah a dir than
   lai, Ka hngalh, ka hngalh, Nunnak Bawipa cu, Vel le thawnnak a sin a um.

[V3]
 Ka umnak inn a remh ti ka hngalh, Ka um ve lai, A umnak ah, A ka
 hramhnak khuaruahhar a si, Kei ca a ra lai, tu hnu ah.

[C3]
   Ka hngalh, ka hngalh, Jesuh a nung than, Vawlei cung ah a dir than
   lai, Ka hngalh, ka hngalh, Nunnak Bawipa cu, Vel le thawnnak a sin a um.</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<title>KA BAWI A NUNG THAN TI KA HNGALH CH146</title>
</song>